results.name: Cube roots arising in A083500.
comment: a(n) < n+1 and a(n) = n+1 over half of the time.
mathematica: Do[k = 0; While[i = n(n + k) + 1; ! IntegerQ[i^(1/3)], k++ ]; Print[i^(1/3)], {n, 1, 75}]
